// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0602 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: ca6d9882-6100-5942-997c-d9d6f3001299

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
